OL,3,C'Part of the family': much-loved Bury
OL,4,Cshop manager says goodbye after 41
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA Bury shop manager is hanging up her
OL,8,Fapron for the final time, after 41
OL,9,Fyears behind the counter at local
OL,10,Fbakery.
OL,12,FAnn Taylor, manager at Greenhalgh's
OL,13,FCraft Bakery began her career at the
OL,14,FPrincess Parade shop in September 1985
OL,15,Fand has been at the heart of the
OL,16,Fbakers ever since.
OL,18,FOver four decades, she has become part
OL,19,Fof the local community, when it moved
OL,20,Fto the Mill Gate shopping centre, and
OL,21,Fhas mentored generations of staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
