OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776668725
OL,3,C'Part of the family': much-loved Bury
OL,4,Cshop manager says goodbye after 41
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThroughout her time at Greenhalgh's,
OL,8,FAnn has helped create a "home away
OL,9,Ffrom home" for both colleagues and
OL,10,Fcustomers alike. Many visitors return
OL,11,Ffor nostalgic treats that remind them
OL,12,Fof sharing special moments with family
OL,13,Facross generations.
OL,15,FAs she prepares to retire, Ann leaves
OL,16,Fbehind not just a successful shop, but
OL,17,Fa lasting legacy within Bury's retail
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
