PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776668725
OL,3,C'Part of the family': much-loved Bury
OL,4,Cshop manager says goodbye after 41
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FCustomers, colleagues, and fellow
OL,8,Ftraders have said she will be 'greatly
OL,9,Fmissed'.
OL,11,FWhat is a Simnel cake?
OL,13,FA Simnel cake is a light fruitcake
OL,14,Fwith a layer of marzipan or almond
OL,15,Fpaste baked into the middle and
OL,16,Fanother layer on top.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776668725
OL,3,C'Part of the family': much-loved Bury
OL,4,Cshop manager says goodbye after 41
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIt's traditionally served at Easter
OL,8,Fand Mothering Sunday, and is often
OL,9,Fdecorated with 11 marzipan balls to
OL,10,Frepresent the apostles, excluding
OL,11,FJudas.
OL,13,FHow does it differ from a Christmas
OL,14,FCake?
OL,16,FSimnel cake is lighter and more
OL,17,Fspringlike, while Christmas cake is
OL,18,Fricher, darker, and usually boozier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
