PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776668725
OL,3,C'Part of the family': much-loved Bury
OL,4,Cshop manager says goodbye after 41
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FSimnel cake is also defined by
OL,8,Fmarzipan baked into the middle and on
OL,9,Ftop, whereas Christmas cake is
OL,10,Ftypically covered in marzipan and
OL,11,Ficing without that signature topping.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
